title: Zombie Football Carnage v1.0
description:
This is: Zombie Football Carnage v1.0

Haven't got to try this yet, but looking at video and screens'll give away what it's about. Nice looking game, lot of score-keeping fun... not sure if it's something to sit down with for hours... but a good time-waster for fun.
--------------------------------------


Description:
Monsters! Monsters everywhere! Fight your way through endless waves of baddies decided to rip you apart.

Key Features:
--Upgrade your gear in the shop and use more than 15 weapons at your disposal to score a bloody touchdown!
--17 different enemies
--13 amazing powerups
--a skill upgrade system
--world leaderboards and as much blood as personality!


System Requirements:
OS: Windows XP or newer.
RAM: 1GB
Processor: Pentium 4 or better.
Graphics Card: DirectX10 compatible hardware.
